itle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 6, "EnglishDescription": "For poor eyesight one should take clean water and if possible clean rainwater and recite on it YAA SHAKOO-RO 41 times then put his eyes in water and open and close the eyes sometimes then will regain his eyesight.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar kisi ki nazar kamzor ho to saaf paani khaas taur par agar baarish ka saaf paani maujood ho to us par 41 martaba YAA SHAKOO-RO ka vird kare aur phir apni aankho’n ko paani mein le ja kar khole bandh kare (aur is tarah se karte rahe) to us ki aankho’n ki binaai (roshni) lout aayegi.", "UrduDescription": "اگر کسی کی نظر کمزور ہو تو صاف پانی خاص طور پر اگر بارش کا صاف پانی موجود ہو تو اس پر 41مرتبہ ’’یَاشَکُوْرُ‘‘ کا دم کرکے اپنی آنکھوں کو پانی میں لے جاکر کھولے بند کرے (اور اس عمل کا تکرار کرے) تو اس کی آنکھوں کی بنائی لوٹ آئے گی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "Arabic